package assignsuchthatsimple01

// The `var x T |= P` statement declares fresh ghost locals that
// satisfy the predicate `P`. Note: Silicon cannot discharge arbitrary
// existential witnesses, so the predicate should be either trivially
// true or should be given triggers based on pure function applications
// so Silicon can find a witness.

func f() {
	var x int |= true
}
